T1  - Do external labor market incentives motivate CEOs to adopt more aggressive corporate tax reporting preferences?
AU  - Kubick, Thomas R.
AU  - Lockhart, G. Brandon
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 36
SP  - 255
EP  - 277
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2016/02/01/
SN  - 0929-1199
